<Layout
	title="About The Setup Vault"
	description="What The Setup Vault is, and our affiliate disclosure."
	pubDate={new Date('July 19 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		The Setup Vault is a resource for people building out a functional, comfortable home
		office — whether that's a first-time setup or a long overdue upgrade. We write practical,
		specific buying guides and comparisons for desk gear: stands, lighting, cable management,
		monitor setups, and the smaller accessories that make a workspace actually work well.
	</p>

	<p>
		Our goal with every article is to give you a genuinely useful, complete answer — not
		filler. We aim to cover real tradeoffs, honest limitations, and the specific details that
		actually matter when you're deciding what to buy.
	</p>

	<h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>

	<p>
		The Setup Vault is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an
		affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising
		fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com.
	</p>

	<p>
		This means that when you click on certain links on this site and make a purchase, we may
		earn a small commission — at no additional cost to you. This applies to every
		"Check current price" link and any other Amazon link found across our articles.
	</p>

	<p>
		We only recommend products we believe are genuinely useful for the topic being covered.
		Our recommendations are not paid placements — commission eligibility does not influence
		which products we choose to write about or how we describe them.
	</p>
</Layout>
